    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every service interval. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and ready for a new home, this is the one. Come see it for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
